WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 3]

02:03.320 --> 02:05.330
Luo Wei grew up in the old town.

02:06.350 --> 02:07.550
She's probably not Xiaowei.

02:08.710 --> 02:10.210
But after she left the old town,

02:10.920 --> 02:12.610
no one has ever seen Luo Wei again.

02:19.440 --> 02:20.180
Maybe...

02:20.950 --> 02:22.790
Xiaowei has taken her form.

02:23.920 --> 02:25.170
The real Luo Wei

02:25.920 --> 02:27.180
might have died long ago.

02:27.750 --> 02:28.890
Xiaowei's a thousand-year fox demon.

02:29.640 --> 02:30.530
Killing Wei Qing

02:31.150 --> 02:31.970
would be easy for her.

02:32.800 --> 02:33.620
She wouldn't need poison.

02:35.560 --> 02:36.420
Maybe...

02:37.640 --> 02:39.580
she's trying to frame someone?

02:40.440 --> 02:41.490
Or perhaps,

02:41.870 --> 02:43.420
for some reason,

02:48.440 --> 02:49.940
she's hesitating to use her magic.

02:55.430 --> 02:56.900
You scared me!

03:04.120 --> 03:05.570
You have Xiaowei's broken tail, right?

03:06.360 --> 03:07.260
Can't you track her?

03:08.710 --> 03:10.380
Only when she uses demon magic

03:10.520 --> 03:11.530
can the tail sense her.

03:11.910 --> 03:13.170
But unless she's desperate,

03:13.630 --> 03:15.340
she won't use her magic.

03:16.910 --> 03:17.500
Why?

03:18.310 --> 03:20.290
Because once she uses it,

03:20.590 --> 03:22.220
the Ice Curse will come after her.

03:24.910 --> 03:25.940
Ice Curse?

03:27.680 --> 03:29.170
Xiaowei once fell in love,

03:29.800 --> 03:30.660
ate human hearts,

03:31.150 --> 03:33.220
and her crimes triggered the punishment.

03:33.960 --> 03:34.610
So now,

03:35.120 --> 03:36.890
the Ice Curse chases her forever.

03:37.960 --> 03:39.290
That's why she cut off her spiritual tail

03:39.800 --> 03:40.730
to hide her demonic energy.

03:44.310 --> 03:45.100
Spiritual tail?

03:46.840 --> 03:48.410
Of the nine-tailed fox's nine tails,

03:48.680 --> 03:49.820
the most important one

03:50.280 --> 03:51.060
is the spiritual tail.

03:51.710 --> 03:53.850
It's also tied to one of the five senses.

03:55.190 --> 03:56.340
Xiaowei's spiritual tail

03:57.280 --> 03:58.540
is linked to her sense of smell.

04:00.710 --> 04:01.540
But last night,

04:01.590 --> 04:02.780
the Ice Curse still appeared.

04:09.960 --> 04:11.170
That means

04:11.840 --> 04:12.820
she used her magic

04:13.400 --> 04:14.220
last night.

04:18.620 --> 04:20.120
[Golden Weave]

04:20.120 --> 04:20.810
Luo Wei!

04:22.000 --> 04:23.850
How dare you poison me!

04:24.310 --> 04:25.540
Get out of the Wei mansion

04:25.560 --> 04:26.540
right now!

04:29.240 --> 04:31.490
I just couldn't bear to see you marry another.

04:32.310 --> 04:33.050
So I wanted you

04:33.070 --> 04:34.220
to fall ill before the wedding,

04:34.560 --> 04:35.410
and call it off.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.580
I prepared an antidote.

04:39.070 --> 04:40.730
I never meant to hurt you.

04:41.240 --> 04:41.980
Wei Qing...

04:42.600 --> 04:43.370
Wei Qing...

04:44.510 --> 04:45.370
Wei Qing...

05:39.120 --> 05:39.930
Yu...

05:41.750 --> 05:42.370
Yu!

05:44.430 --> 05:45.660
Oh no!

05:47.800 --> 05:49.900
I'm under a death curse! What do we do?

05:52.000 --> 05:53.340
Do you know what to do?

05:54.310 --> 05:55.050
You don't.

05:55.680 --> 05:56.700
Why aren't you saying anything?

05:57.430 --> 05:58.340
You can't talk.

05:59.560 --> 06:00.220
Yu!

06:08.750 --> 06:09.410
Yu!

06:09.870 --> 06:10.490
Ms. Yu,

06:10.680 --> 06:11.290
your sachet!

06:12.870 --> 06:13.540
Yu!

06:23.870 --> 06:25.410
The Wei family is really lively.

06:26.120 --> 06:27.490
There's a good show every day.

06:28.510 --> 06:29.900
Shengwei...

06:32.340 --> 06:34.780
[Shengwei]

06:36.600 --> 06:37.220
Let go of me!

06:39.120 --> 06:40.850
I'm packing up and going back to my parents' today.

06:41.190 --> 06:41.850
Are you crazy?

06:42.630 --> 06:43.980
We just got married,

06:44.070 --> 06:45.170
and now you want to leave?

06:45.600 --> 06:46.820
Do you want me to become

06:46.830 --> 06:48.100
the laughingstock of all Luo'an city?

06:48.240 --> 06:48.860
Wei Qing,

06:49.510 --> 06:50.610
when I saw you and Steward Luo

06:50.610 --> 06:51.850
holding each other just now,

06:52.000 --> 06:52.810
I woke up.

06:55.360 --> 06:56.020
What I felt for you

06:56.510 --> 06:57.540
was just a fleeting crush,

06:59.510 --> 07:00.490
not real love.

07:00.750 --> 07:02.100
You married into this family,

07:02.160 --> 07:03.370
so you belong to the Weis now.

07:03.680 --> 07:04.940
You don't have to love me,

07:05.190 --> 07:07.020
but you can't bring shame to this family.

07:07.630 --> 07:09.680
If you want to leave,

07:10.310 --> 07:11.700
you'll have to be carried out dead!

07:14.240 --> 07:15.580
How did you become like this?

07:17.390 --> 07:20.250
I was so blind back then!

07:20.950 --> 07:21.580
Sorry!

07:25.950 --> 07:26.580
Am I interrupting?

07:27.680 --> 07:28.250
Ms. Yu,

07:28.720 --> 07:29.370
just now,

07:29.600 --> 07:30.660
you dropped your sachet.

07:48.190 --> 07:49.730
This is the token of love you gave me.

07:54.310 --> 07:55.170
Here, I'm returning it.

07:56.510 --> 07:57.140
From now on,

07:57.920 --> 07:59.020
we're even!

08:01.160 --> 08:01.780
Fine!

08:03.430 --> 08:04.490
You said it.

08:05.270 --> 08:06.490
We're done!

08:17.510 --> 08:18.220
What a mess.

08:34.260 --> 08:41.220
[Clouds hide the moon, but not my love. This silent heart, so hard to speak.]

09:33.600 --> 09:34.340
Mr. Liu,

09:36.030 --> 09:36.890
looking for something?

09:39.510 --> 09:41.180
I heard my cousin and his wife had a fight,

09:41.630 --> 09:42.650
and their love token got lost.

09:43.510 --> 09:45.010
So I came to help look for it.

09:46.630 --> 09:47.370
I don't get it.

09:49.030 --> 09:49.980
A couple

09:50.750 --> 09:52.420
fights and makes up in no time.

09:53.510 --> 09:54.980
Angry words can be taken back,

09:55.840 --> 09:57.100
but a lost love token

09:58.000 --> 09:59.060
is gone forever.

10:00.910 --> 10:02.100
What I don't get

10:02.910 --> 10:03.770
is you.

10:06.030 --> 10:06.700
What do you mean?

10:08.390 --> 10:09.300
Look,

10:09.510 --> 10:11.490
you secretly care for Steward Luo

10:11.910 --> 10:12.890
and wish her happiness.

10:13.790 --> 10:15.870
So why not help her leave Wei Qing?

10:17.030 --> 10:18.770
But by looking for that token,

10:18.790 --> 10:19.430
it seems

10:19.720 --> 10:22.060
you want them to patch things up.

10:23.510 --> 10:24.340
Mr. Liu,

10:25.790 --> 10:27.060
who exactly

10:28.440 --> 10:29.530
are you trying to protect?

10:34.600 --> 10:36.490
My beloved, of course.

10:41.510 --> 10:42.250
Maybe...

10:43.120 --> 10:44.340
I'm just a selfish man

10:44.360 --> 10:45.370
at heart,

10:46.390 --> 10:47.700
who doesn't want to see her

10:48.510 --> 10:49.850
in someone else's arms.

10:57.200 --> 10:58.060
Your hands

10:58.550 --> 11:00.700
are covered in tiny cuts.

11:01.630 --> 11:03.370
Looks like they were pricked

11:03.380 --> 11:04.220
by something sharp.

11:05.910 --> 11:06.770
Were you cut

11:07.960 --> 11:09.580
by flower leaves

11:10.440 --> 11:11.820
while looking for the token?

11:12.320 --> 11:13.010
It's nothing.

11:14.150 --> 11:15.580
I've trained in martial arts

11:15.750 --> 11:16.580
since childhood.

11:17.200 --> 11:18.100
Little scratches like this

11:18.910 --> 11:19.950
are no big deal.

11:21.080 --> 11:22.380
Still,

11:22.840 --> 11:24.010
you should be careful.

11:27.090 --> 11:27.840
This way!

11:28.150 --> 11:28.980
Someone!

11:30.120 --> 11:31.130
You, search the east courtyard. Quick!

11:31.710 --> 11:32.360
Hurry!

11:33.910 --> 11:34.890
You, search the west courtyard!

11:36.600 --> 11:37.700
Quick! This way!

11:39.200 --> 11:39.940
This way...

11:40.790 --> 11:42.100
Master Wei is missing!

11:42.320 --> 11:43.100
His life's at risk!

11:43.320 --> 11:44.610
What are you all dawdling for?

11:44.770 --> 11:45.660
Search, now!

11:45.960 --> 11:46.440
Search!

11:46.440 --> 11:47.070
Understood.

11:54.960 --> 11:55.700
Uh-oh.

11:56.000 --> 11:56.610
Master Wei,

11:57.200 --> 11:58.490
mind being bait

11:58.750 --> 12:00.010
to lure Xiaowei out?

12:31.080 --> 12:32.130
Time for the show!

12:37.200 --> 12:39.490
All you demon hunters

12:39.550 --> 12:40.340
are just useless!

12:41.080 --> 12:42.220
A whole day's gone,

12:42.550 --> 12:43.610
and my cousin's still not found!

12:49.510 --> 12:50.650
Can you smell the fragrance?

12:57.550 --> 12:58.700
The death curse is spreading further.

12:59.630 --> 13:01.130
It might've reached our sense of smell.

13:27.080 --> 13:29.070
"See me in the afternoon at the weaving workshop,

13:29.350 --> 13:31.080
and the deadlock will be solved."

13:33.870 --> 13:34.800
Steward Luo,

13:35.670 --> 13:37.330
why did you go there yesterday?

13:48.670 --> 13:49.730
Where's Miss Yu Wei?

13:50.790 --> 13:51.980
She's missing too?

14:03.670 --> 14:04.390
Mr. Liu,

14:05.030 --> 14:06.110
I asked around.

14:06.320 --> 14:08.330
No one's seen you

14:08.510 --> 14:09.650
since last evening.

14:11.000 --> 14:11.650
May I ask,

14:12.910 --> 14:14.530
where were you last night?

14:15.630 --> 14:16.420
I was asleep.

14:17.440 --> 14:18.220
At dusk,

14:18.270 --> 14:19.820
my bedding got dirty,

14:20.320 --> 14:21.340
so I asked Steward Luo

14:21.440 --> 14:22.300
to change it for a new set.

14:22.720 --> 14:23.940
She can vouch for me.

14:24.600 --> 14:25.530
Steward Luo,

14:26.320 --> 14:27.700
you even handle little things like this?

14:29.390 --> 14:30.850
Mr. Liu's been pampered since childhood,

14:31.320 --> 14:33.340
and only sleeps on silk-satin bedding.

14:34.440 --> 14:36.420
Those beddings are locked in the storeroom,

14:37.200 --> 14:38.490
and only I have the key.

14:40.670 --> 14:42.130
You all keep saying

14:42.170 --> 14:43.340
this is the work of demons.

14:44.380 --> 14:46.100
So why question us mortals?

14:48.320 --> 14:49.010
You, Wu!

14:49.910 --> 14:51.420
Didn't you promise a barrier

14:51.790 --> 14:52.940
to protect this household?

14:54.030 --> 14:55.420
All for show.

14:56.910 --> 14:57.490
The way I see it,

14:57.510 --> 14:59.010
you're no folk demon hunters.

14:59.870 --> 15:00.850
You're just frauds!

15:01.930 --> 15:04.130
- I... - Barriers only stop demons,

15:04.960 --> 15:06.300
not the evil in men's hearts.

15:07.000 --> 15:08.200
Master Wei's disappearance

15:08.510 --> 15:10.100
has nothing to do with demon magic.

15:25.120 --> 15:26.700
Someone used a spell in the workshop.

15:39.200 --> 15:40.490
The formation's been triggered!

16:16.440 --> 16:17.980
Hello there, Xiaowei.

16:52.270 --> 16:52.850
Thanks a lot!

16:53.240 --> 16:54.250
This fox demon's no easy catch.

17:26.070 --> 17:27.050
Miss Yu Wei?

17:27.720 --> 17:28.530
How could it be her?

17:35.550 --> 17:36.530
Hard to accept?

17:38.400 --> 17:39.620
She is Xiaowei?

17:45.880 --> 17:47.490
I'll take her back for questioning!

17:48.090 --> 17:48.850
Li Jie!

17:52.980 --> 17:53.620
No.

17:54.360 --> 17:55.390
My sect has hunted Xiaowei

17:55.390 --> 17:56.490
for many years.

17:56.890 --> 17:57.860
I can't hand her over.

17:58.920 --> 17:59.730
That's true.

18:00.550 --> 18:01.010
However,

18:01.510 --> 18:02.810
the Xiaowei you're looking for

18:03.110 --> 18:04.290
is the eight-tailed fox

18:04.350 --> 18:05.370
with one tail broken.

18:05.570 --> 18:07.220
Take a closer look at this one.

18:17.720 --> 18:19.490
Nine... nine tails...

19:15.750 --> 19:16.380
Just as I thought.

19:21.270 --> 19:22.090
Help!

19:26.160 --> 19:26.980
Help!

19:42.350 --> 19:43.770
You said you never lie, huh?

19:49.350 --> 19:50.090
Trying to run?

20:12.000 --> 20:13.330
Miss Yu Wei, wake up!

21:25.000 --> 21:26.140
A double-flower hunter!

21:27.550 --> 21:28.220
Mo Yuntan!

22:11.590 --> 22:13.050
By heavenly law, return to source.

22:14.190 --> 22:14.840
Disperse!

22:19.880 --> 22:21.730
The double-flower hunter is truly impressive.

23:33.550 --> 23:34.180
Wei Qing.

23:36.070 --> 23:36.810
I was so worried about you.

23:37.240 --> 23:37.900
Are you okay?

23:38.400 --> 23:39.290
Why are you all disheveled?

23:39.440 --> 23:40.010
Where's your belt?

23:41.160 --> 23:41.860
Steward Luo said

23:41.920 --> 23:43.250
Master Wei's belt was broken,

23:43.550 --> 23:45.090
so she took it to mend.

23:52.030 --> 23:53.220
You are...?

23:54.830 --> 23:55.860
I'm Mo Yuntan,

23:56.550 --> 23:59.050
a demon hunter from the Shilin Sect.

24:00.920 --> 24:03.090
A... double-flower hunter!

24:24.070 --> 24:24.940
With my binding seal,

24:25.640 --> 24:26.660
the blood of origin,

24:27.830 --> 24:28.860
all can be traced.

24:52.310 --> 24:53.050
Found them?

24:55.880 --> 24:56.810
But you said

24:57.110 --> 24:58.960
even if they fled to the ends of the earth,

24:59.880 --> 25:01.330
as long as they're still in this world,

25:01.830 --> 25:02.660
your Blood Binding Seal

25:03.310 --> 25:04.940
could definitely track them.

25:05.350 --> 25:06.500
They must have gone

25:06.500 --> 25:07.890
to a place more distant

25:08.310 --> 25:10.010
than the ends of the earth.

25:11.270 --> 25:12.810
Is there such a place in the world?

25:13.110 --> 25:13.900
There is.

25:18.110 --> 25:18.940
The Formless Moon Palace.

25:24.510 --> 25:25.220
Legend has it

25:25.640 --> 25:27.140
Nuwa used spring water and clay

25:28.070 --> 25:29.570
to shape all beings.

25:30.070 --> 25:31.010
And since ancient times,

25:31.750 --> 25:32.730
that water's been guarded

25:32.790 --> 25:34.490
by seven nine-tailed foxes

25:34.550 --> 25:35.380
who are immortal.

25:37.110 --> 25:38.140
This sacred spring's location

25:39.510 --> 25:41.220
is called the Formless Moon Palace.

25:46.000 --> 25:46.620
Wangyan,

25:48.000 --> 25:49.490
we're back at the Sacred Spring.

25:50.960 --> 25:51.700
Why are you

25:54.000 --> 25:55.050
still nervous?

25:56.070 --> 25:58.810
Luckily tonight's the full moon,

25:59.640 --> 26:00.890
forcing us back

26:00.890 --> 26:02.490
by the Decree's power.

26:03.590 --> 26:04.290
Otherwise,

26:05.070 --> 26:06.530
that double-flower hunter

26:06.550 --> 26:07.660
would've been hard to handle.

26:08.510 --> 26:10.280
I don't think

26:10.280 --> 26:11.540
he's that great.

26:12.640 --> 26:14.490
If my magic hadn't gone out of control,

26:14.720 --> 26:16.770
he'd be no match for us.

26:17.640 --> 26:18.530
Don't underestimate him.

26:20.590 --> 26:21.380
Fine.

26:23.510 --> 26:24.330
Whatever you say.

26:31.030 --> 26:32.830
Let's start the memory sharing.

27:15.160 --> 27:16.730
You're not Master Wei either.

27:16.770 --> 27:17.750
Master Wei

27:17.750 --> 27:19.030
wouldn't hold a knife to me.

27:19.030 --> 27:20.180
Such a beautiful vase,

27:20.310 --> 27:20.980
and you have no taste for elegance.

27:21.000 --> 27:22.230
Has it truly been so long

27:22.230 --> 27:22.890
Darling,

27:22.890 --> 27:24.180
- that you've forgotten my face? - why are you in such a hurry?

27:24.200 --> 27:24.810
My name is Ji Ling.

27:25.160 --> 27:26.010
Ji means "life's a journey,"

27:26.110 --> 27:26.940
and Ling means "hearts that beat as one."

27:31.340 --> 27:31.860
[Wei]

27:34.400 --> 27:34.910
Disperse!

28:15.590 --> 28:16.420
Formless Moon Sect...

28:20.830 --> 28:22.490
I once read some fragments

28:22.880 --> 28:23.590
about ancient times

28:23.590 --> 28:24.730
in the Dragon Deity's library.

28:25.240 --> 28:26.180
They say

28:26.270 --> 28:27.810
this sect, like the Dragon Deity,

28:28.200 --> 28:29.860
has existed since ancient times.

28:31.830 --> 28:33.190
It belongs to the nine-tailed fox clan,

28:33.310 --> 28:34.630
appointed by Goddess Nuwa

28:35.070 --> 28:36.140
to wander the world,

28:36.680 --> 28:37.530
benefit all things,

28:38.110 --> 28:39.380
and uphold justice.

28:40.310 --> 28:41.490
They say this sect

28:42.030 --> 28:43.660
reveals itself only to the fated,

28:44.270 --> 28:45.900
opens only to the summoned.

28:46.590 --> 28:49.330
Everything in this world can be traced,

28:49.680 --> 28:50.730
but that place alone

28:51.510 --> 28:52.660
leaves no trace.

28:53.550 --> 28:55.900
So Xiaowei betrayed her sect,

28:56.750 --> 28:57.490
and she's been hunted

28:57.510 --> 28:58.900
by the Ice Curse.

28:59.440 --> 29:00.660
Seems Wu Wangyan and Yu Wei

29:00.720 --> 29:02.080
were sent by this sect

29:02.160 --> 29:03.490
to capture the traitor Xiaowei.

29:05.440 --> 29:06.050
Well,

29:06.920 --> 29:08.380
I have other tasks to handle.

29:09.510 --> 29:10.140
Everyone,

29:11.030 --> 29:12.180
please be extra careful.

29:28.030 --> 29:30.180
I didn't think Xiaowei would be so cruel,

29:31.400 --> 29:32.660
tricking me into the formation

29:33.440 --> 29:34.730
to be her scapegoat.

29:39.240 --> 29:40.860
But when was I exposed?

29:42.440 --> 29:44.940
Did you use the Word Magic on anyone?

29:48.790 --> 29:50.570
I know it's been a while,

29:50.790 --> 29:52.220
but you really don't recognize me?

29:52.750 --> 29:53.900
So she's Xiaowei.

29:57.160 --> 29:58.660
No wonder she's named Yu Shengwei.

29:59.640 --> 30:01.330
She can't let go of the character "Wei."

30:01.920 --> 30:03.620
Maybe it's not that simple.

30:04.440 --> 30:06.560
I used the Word Magic on her too.

30:07.880 --> 30:08.620
Quiet.

30:10.070 --> 30:11.490
Xiaowei's Word Magic

30:11.510 --> 30:12.620
is unmatched.

30:13.270 --> 30:14.420
If she were really Xiaowei,

30:14.750 --> 30:16.660
I would've suffered backlash then.

30:20.830 --> 30:21.810
Maybe...

30:22.920 --> 30:24.660
the Yu Shengwei we met then

30:24.680 --> 30:25.420
was real.

30:26.350 --> 30:27.220
You're...

30:28.310 --> 30:29.010
Rucui.

30:29.510 --> 30:30.530
Is it time yet?

30:31.270 --> 30:33.250
But the woman sneaking back later

30:34.270 --> 30:35.250
might be a different one.

30:46.440 --> 30:47.290
Or maybe...

30:49.590 --> 30:51.770
when I used the Word Magic on Yu Shengwei,

30:53.720 --> 30:55.050
Xiaowei was also there,

30:55.590 --> 30:56.620
and she noticed.

30:58.110 --> 30:59.140
Oh, you're Yu Wei.

31:07.400 --> 31:08.050
That makes sense.

31:09.590 --> 31:10.330
Wei Qing,

31:10.790 --> 31:11.730
Luo Wei,

31:12.200 --> 31:14.090
Yu Shengwei, Liu Weixue...

31:14.830 --> 31:16.330
It's a bit too coincidental, right?

31:16.680 --> 31:18.230
Everyone's name

31:18.720 --> 31:20.670
has a word that sounds like "Wei."

31:34.920 --> 31:36.380
Thanks for saving me earlier.

31:37.310 --> 31:37.980
These past few days

31:38.550 --> 31:39.730
must've drained your energy.

31:40.510 --> 31:41.290
Have some walnuts.

31:42.400 --> 31:43.490
It was nothing.

31:44.200 --> 31:45.050
No need to be so polite,

31:45.440 --> 31:46.180
Master Ji Ling.

31:46.510 --> 31:47.570
Yeah, no need.

31:48.510 --> 31:49.980
You didn't manage to save him, right?

31:50.750 --> 31:52.380
You almost got yourself caught instead.

31:53.000 --> 31:53.980
We're actually saved

31:54.400 --> 31:56.010
by Shilin Sect's double-flower hunter,

31:56.110 --> 31:56.810
Mo Yuntan.

31:58.160 --> 31:58.730
Li Jie,

31:59.070 --> 31:59.810
stop it.

32:00.240 --> 32:01.490
Save him some face, will you?

32:13.350 --> 32:14.380
It's tasteless.

32:17.000 --> 32:17.940
Without my sense of taste,

32:19.160 --> 32:20.620
I'd rather be dead!

32:24.000 --> 32:24.870
Well, that wish

32:24.870 --> 32:25.900
might come true soon.

32:27.960 --> 32:29.490
We've already lost three senses.

32:29.880 --> 32:30.660
In two more days,

32:31.110 --> 32:32.570
if we still haven't caught Xiaowei,

32:33.080 --> 32:34.180
the curse

32:34.750 --> 32:36.010
will consume us entirely.

33:09.110 --> 33:10.330
It's the dead of night!

33:11.070 --> 33:12.140
What are you up to?

33:12.640 --> 33:13.530
Do me a favor.

33:16.310 --> 33:16.810
Spit it out.

33:17.350 --> 33:18.140
What do you want me to steal?

33:20.510 --> 33:21.900
You know yourself well, huh?

33:25.680 --> 33:27.050
I need you to sneak into Weimiao Pavilion

33:27.510 --> 33:28.260
and steal those slips

33:28.260 --> 33:29.890
filled with secrets

33:30.310 --> 33:30.940
from the donation box.

33:32.790 --> 33:34.230
The walls there are too high,

33:34.350 --> 33:35.230
and a barrier's set.

33:35.310 --> 33:36.220
I can't get in.

33:38.110 --> 33:39.010
I've got it figured out.

33:40.030 --> 33:40.810
This mission

33:41.310 --> 33:42.140
is perfect for you.

33:44.110 --> 33:44.940
By the wall,

33:45.590 --> 33:46.380
there's a dog hole.

33:54.350 --> 33:54.730
Madame.

33:56.030 --> 33:56.490
Madame.

34:01.310 --> 34:02.090
You may go.

34:02.440 --> 34:02.770
Yes.

34:05.960 --> 34:07.010
Such a big kite!

34:08.110 --> 34:09.330
Much has happened lately,

34:09.680 --> 34:10.330
and the household's been unsettled.

34:10.830 --> 34:12.220
My husband got so scared,

34:12.360 --> 34:13.490
he's been losing his spirit.

34:13.840 --> 34:15.020
Back in my hometown,

34:15.540 --> 34:17.650
they say when bad things happen,

34:18.000 --> 34:19.610
we can buy a kite and fly it away.

34:19.840 --> 34:20.980
The higher the kite flies,

34:21.230 --> 34:23.300
the further the bad luck goes.

34:23.670 --> 34:25.380
So I picked the biggest one.

34:27.510 --> 34:29.240
A kite this size

34:30.000 --> 34:31.130
must've been hard to find.

34:33.150 --> 34:33.980
Yeah.

34:35.360 --> 34:36.490
But I got lucky

34:36.920 --> 34:37.780
and actually found one.

34:39.190 --> 34:39.860
Maybe...

34:40.190 --> 34:41.170
it was a blessing

34:41.710 --> 34:42.780
from above.

34:44.320 --> 34:45.650
Didn't she and Wei Qing

34:46.190 --> 34:47.490
fight and talk about divorce earlier?

34:48.030 --> 34:49.490
They're back together so soon,

34:50.150 --> 34:51.420
and she's so concerned about him?

34:52.800 --> 34:53.530
A couple

34:53.840 --> 34:55.300
just make up anytime.

34:55.360 --> 34:56.210
Isn't that normal?

34:56.590 --> 34:57.780
You have experience?

34:58.550 --> 35:00.490
I... I really don't.

35:03.960 --> 35:04.570
Ms. Yu.

35:06.110 --> 35:06.740
Master Wu.

35:09.920 --> 35:10.740
Lately,

35:11.440 --> 35:13.210
you've been so dedicated

35:13.630 --> 35:14.660
to hunting demons.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.380
You flatter me.

35:16.920 --> 35:17.860
It's my duty.

35:20.150 --> 35:21.100
What I meant was

35:21.760 --> 35:24.220
that smell on you...

35:24.550 --> 35:25.260
You haven't

35:25.550 --> 35:27.380
had time to bathe lately?

35:31.190 --> 35:32.020
Oh, I get it now.

35:33.760 --> 35:34.420
This smell is...

35:34.510 --> 35:35.530
You're up early, guys!

35:38.880 --> 35:39.530
Master Wu,

35:40.510 --> 35:41.490
go wash up.

35:43.710 --> 35:44.980
You even smell it from that far?

35:47.070 --> 35:47.860
It really stinks.

35:49.510 --> 35:50.490
Come on, smell again.

35:52.190 --> 35:53.210
Just go bathe already!

35:54.630 --> 35:55.340
Fine,

35:56.400 --> 35:57.420
if you say so.

36:03.030 --> 36:04.300
You almost got me killed!

36:05.400 --> 36:06.610
Every night, they move that box

36:06.710 --> 36:07.380
from the courtyard

36:07.400 --> 36:08.650
into Lady Wei's bedroom.

36:09.440 --> 36:10.980
Good thing I'm quick!

36:15.070 --> 36:15.780
But man,

36:16.670 --> 36:18.090
Lady Wei is really something.

36:19.070 --> 36:21.010
His bed's all covered in silk-satin.

36:25.510 --> 36:26.570
So comfy!

36:32.320 --> 36:34.050
I nearly stayed there forever.

37:18.230 --> 37:19.010
Sister,

37:19.510 --> 37:21.550
are Mother and Father asleep?

37:21.920 --> 37:23.650
Why can't I wake them up?

37:25.320 --> 37:26.680
You're the child

37:26.680 --> 37:27.820
of a human and a demon.

37:29.900 --> 37:31.420
You can't cultivate normally

37:32.190 --> 37:33.570
or control your wild nature.

37:35.190 --> 37:36.130
When you grow up,

37:37.190 --> 37:38.530
you'll bring disaster to the world.

37:52.110 --> 37:53.170
Don't blame me...

38:15.760 --> 38:17.050
Are you a folk demon hunter?

38:20.550 --> 38:21.860
I'm from the Shilin Sect.

38:22.550 --> 38:24.370
There's a half-demon child here,

38:24.510 --> 38:25.340
very dangerous.

38:28.510 --> 38:29.490
It's already gone.

38:33.550 --> 38:34.260
You did the right thing.

38:35.000 --> 38:36.530
Or when she grows up,

38:37.360 --> 38:38.690
she'll keep hurting those around her,

38:39.400 --> 38:40.490
and suffer herself.

38:45.230 --> 38:46.300
Why are you crying?

38:48.590 --> 38:49.530
Because the flowers...

38:52.760 --> 38:53.490
they withered.

38:56.670 --> 38:58.170
Though that joke's quite lame,

38:58.760 --> 39:00.260
I'll still laugh, I guess.

39:12.800 --> 39:14.090
Do you like flowers?

39:15.960 --> 39:16.690
Yes.

39:18.360 --> 39:20.490
Flowers just bloom and fade.

39:21.230 --> 39:21.940
No need to cry.

39:22.960 --> 39:23.900
In this world,

39:24.320 --> 39:25.610
there's plenty to be upset about.

39:26.400 --> 39:27.210
Save your tears

39:27.760 --> 39:29.300
for what truly makes you sad.

39:30.510 --> 39:32.090
If you have none left for those moments,

39:33.150 --> 39:34.260
it will be even worse.

39:42.960 --> 39:44.420
I'm pretty sad right now.

39:47.940 --> 39:50.460
♪Who calls my name so clear♪

39:50.780 --> 39:53.100
♪Chasing shadows of the years...♪

39:53.360 --> 39:54.340
Let me take you somewhere.

39:54.710 --> 39:55.780
You won't be sad there.

39:56.700 --> 39:58.700
♪To give her tomorrow fair♪

39:58.780 --> 40:01.900
♪Tears and joy pile high and wide♪

40:02.020 --> 40:04.340
♪Moonlight bathes her face tonight♪

40:04.420 --> 40:10.300
♪Don't let dew fade before the light♪

40:14.670 --> 40:15.380
Awake?

40:29.190 --> 40:30.300
Time to head back to the Wei mansion.

40:31.320 --> 40:32.380
We caused

40:32.440 --> 40:33.740
such a big scene last time.

40:34.710 --> 40:35.570
How do we face

40:36.400 --> 40:38.640
Wu Shiguang and Li Jie?

40:40.670 --> 40:41.980
We might end up fighting again.

40:43.510 --> 40:45.460
Why deliberately avoid mentioning Ji Ling?

40:49.590 --> 40:50.300
Him?

40:51.710 --> 40:52.530
He's easy to win over.

40:52.960 --> 40:54.260
Don't underestimate him.

40:55.110 --> 40:56.610
The words "fated one"

40:56.800 --> 40:57.980
are no joke.

40:59.830 --> 41:01.170
You're pretending

41:01.210 --> 41:02.170
not to remember him, right?

41:07.920 --> 41:08.910
Wangyan...

41:09.150 --> 41:11.070
During the memory sharing earlier,

41:11.150 --> 41:12.500
I saw it clearly.

41:16.150 --> 41:17.210
Besides you,

41:18.710 --> 41:19.490
Ji Ling

41:20.800 --> 41:22.110
is the second person

41:22.110 --> 41:23.350
who truly made me happy.

41:25.070 --> 41:26.130
Just a tiny bit.

41:26.220 --> 41:29.820
♪Clouds we watched drift in the skies♪

41:30.220 --> 41:37.180
♪Wind blows soft, our voices dry♪

41:43.190 --> 41:44.420
So many secrets!

41:45.880 --> 41:47.780
Why are so many people praying for love?

41:48.840 --> 41:50.050
What's so great

41:50.230 --> 41:51.010
about love?

41:51.840 --> 41:52.260
Hah.

41:56.110 --> 41:57.090
How did you get these?

41:57.920 --> 41:59.340
It took me a lot of work.

42:01.110 --> 42:01.820
I'm so exhausted.

42:02.230 --> 42:03.570
Wu Shiguang, have you no shame?

42:08.150 --> 42:09.740
Why is Xiaowei collecting these secrets?

42:10.840 --> 42:12.740
It's probably her way of cultivating.

42:13.190 --> 42:14.820
Demons have many cultivation paths.

42:15.150 --> 42:16.130
Low-rank demons

42:16.190 --> 42:17.900
suck the essence and blood of mortals.

42:18.550 --> 42:19.670
Higher-rank ones

42:19.760 --> 42:20.980
bathe in the essence of the sun and moon.

42:21.550 --> 42:23.580
But Jiu Ying, the king of all demons,

42:23.630 --> 42:25.110
feeds on the hatred and fear

42:25.110 --> 42:26.300
of humans.

42:26.710 --> 42:28.690
The more suffering and chaos,

42:29.000 --> 42:29.900
the stronger it becomes.

42:30.880 --> 42:33.420
The opposite is the Dragon Deity.

42:34.110 --> 42:36.530
People make wishes and fulfill vows to him.

42:36.920 --> 42:38.570
He also gains more power

42:39.030 --> 42:40.820
from their offerings,

42:41.280 --> 42:42.650
worship, and love

42:43.710 --> 42:44.860
to bless all beings.

42:45.550 --> 42:46.490
And so it goes,

42:46.840 --> 42:48.490
justice and kindness in the world

42:48.800 --> 42:50.050
keep growing more and more.

42:51.590 --> 42:52.090
Impressive.

42:55.920 --> 42:56.900
All beings

42:57.880 --> 42:58.610
have their secrets.

42:59.360 --> 43:00.490
Like love and hate,

43:01.360 --> 43:02.420
they are endless,

43:02.800 --> 43:04.010
a resource without limit.

43:06.000 --> 43:08.130
This thousand-year fox demon really is something.

43:08.510 --> 43:11.130
So how do we find

43:13.190 --> 43:14.980
Luo Wei's secret?

43:23.590 --> 43:24.170
Look!

43:27.670 --> 43:28.740
"All merchants are sly.

43:29.360 --> 43:30.380
That's how business works.

43:30.380 --> 43:31.300
[All merchants are sly. That's how business works. By Wei Qing]

43:31.550 --> 43:32.300
By Wei Qing."

43:34.230 --> 43:35.650
Wei Qing also prayed for a love talisman?

43:38.400 --> 43:39.260
For Ms. Yu?

43:40.550 --> 43:41.380
No wonder.

43:42.110 --> 43:43.940
Forget love at first sight.

43:44.320 --> 43:45.860
It was all a setup.

43:46.280 --> 43:48.010
This talisman did the trick.

43:48.760 --> 43:49.300
Oh no!

43:49.550 --> 43:50.340
Ms. Yu's in danger!

43:58.540 --> 44:02.380
["... close friend. By Luo Wei"]

44:12.880 --> 44:15.210
She tricked...

44:15.510 --> 44:16.010
Master Wei!

44:16.840 --> 44:17.860
- She tricked me. - Master Wei!

44:19.710 --> 44:20.420
Master Wei!

44:32.230 --> 44:32.690
Yu!

44:33.150 --> 44:34.530
Ms. Yu, your sachet!

44:45.550 --> 44:47.330
Isn't it Ms. Yu's sachet?

44:48.030 --> 44:48.610
Wei Qing,

44:49.920 --> 44:50.780
Yu Shengwei...

45:11.110 --> 45:12.170
This talisman has two layers.

45:15.980 --> 45:19.100
[Yu Shengwei; Wei Qing]

45:23.550 --> 45:24.340
This isn't the one

45:24.400 --> 45:25.490
Wei Qing got for Ms. Yu.

45:29.440 --> 45:30.740
This is Luo Wei's talisman.

45:32.440 --> 45:33.530
They were secretly swapped.

45:35.510 --> 45:36.690
He kept saying

45:36.960 --> 45:38.170
she tricked him.

45:39.000 --> 45:39.940
Who is that "she"?

45:40.760 --> 45:42.300
Only Xiaowei knows, I'm afraid.

45:44.670 --> 45:45.170
Not surprising.

45:46.000 --> 45:47.170
Fox demons are the best at lying.

46:40.380 --> 46:41.540
♪It's your light♪

46:41.740 --> 46:43.620
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:43.780 --> 46:46.900
♪That set the night alight♪

46:47.260 --> 46:53.780
♪And lead me through the fight♪

46:55.540 --> 46:57.420
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

46:57.860 --> 47:02.300
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

47:03.100 --> 47:04.780
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

47:04.940 --> 47:10.340
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

47:11.100 --> 47:16.500
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

47:18.820 --> 47:24.860
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

47:25.820 --> 47:27.980
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

47:28.260 --> 47:33.100
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

47:33.460 --> 47:35.780
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

47:35.980 --> 47:41.060
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

47:41.300 --> 47:43.300
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

47:43.580 --> 47:47.940
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

47:48.940 --> 47:55.900
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

48:12.460 --> 48:15.420
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

48:16.500 --> 48:19.900
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

48:20.700 --> 48:23.220
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

48:23.460 --> 48:26.540
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

48:26.940 --> 48:29.260
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

48:29.780 --> 48:34.180
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

48:34.420 --> 48:36.580
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

48:36.980 --> 48:41.940
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

48:42.180 --> 48:43.340
♪It's your light♪

48:43.540 --> 48:45.380
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

48:45.580 --> 48:48.700
♪That set the night alight♪

48:49.460 --> 48:58.900
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
